[local variables]
caves  : (table) module variable
layers : (list) unused
init   : (boolean) is this module initialised
n_layer: (int) the amount of active cave layers

cave_gen_settings: (MapGenSettings) settings for generating caves

[module functions]
add_layer: add a new cave below the last one
init     : initialise the module
move_up  : move the player up 1 layer
move_down: move the player down 1 layer